玩唔得，係全Game最大敗筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n整體偏向RPG\b又唔夠豐富，根本冇RPG最重要既&quot;打寶&quot;，武將太依賴升LV，做城下町任又冇經驗（做任冇經冇寶，做黎做乜）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}